    	</p>
      
      <div class="card--3rows">
        <div class="card card1">
          	<div class="card-header">
        		<h3>US &amp; Canada</h3>
            </div>
          	<div class="card-body">
        		<p class="card-body-subtitle">Return Period</p>
        		<p class="large-body-text">Free returns &amp; exchanges within 30 days.</p>
      		</div>
          	<div class="card-footer">
